\c 11 Jefuta 1 Zvino Jefuta muGireadhi, wakanga ari munhu ane simba noumhare, asi wakanga ari mwanakomana wechifeve; Gireadhi ndiye wakabereka Jefuta. 2 Mukadzi waGireadhi akamuberekera vanakomana; zvino vanakomana vomukadzi wake vakati vakura, vakadzinga Jefuta, vakati kwaari, "Haungadyi nhaka mumba mababa vedu, nokuti uri mwanakomana womumwe mukadzi." 3 Ipapo Jefuta akatiza vanunguna vake, akandogara panyika yeTobhi; varume vakaipa vakaunganira kuna Jefuta, vakasibuda naye kundorwa. 4 Zvino nguva yakati yapfuura, vana vaAmoni vakandorwa navalsiraeri, 5 Zvino vana vaAmoni vakati vorwa navaIsiraeri, vakuru veGireadhi vakandotora Jefuta panyika yeTobhi. 6 Vakati kuna Jefuta, "Uya, uve ishe wedu, kuti tindorwa navana vaAmoni." 7 Jefuta akati kuvakuru veGireadhi, "Hamuna kundivenga mukandidzinga mumba mababa vangu here? Zvino mauyireiko kwandiri, zvamava munjodzi?"
